            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-orange-700 dark:group-hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors duration-300">Electronics Design</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Custom circuit design and PCB development for specialized applications.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-orange-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Analog & digital circuit design</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-orange-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Multi-layer PCB layout</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-orange-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Power supply design</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-orange-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Signal integrity optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white/95 to-blue-50/50 dark:from-neutral-900/95 dark:to-blue-950/40 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-blue-200/40 dark:border-blue-800/40 hover:shadow-2xl hover:scale-[1.05] hover:border-blue-300/70 transition-all duration-500">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/15 to-blue-600/35 dark:from-blue-400/25 dark:to-blue-500/45 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 ring-2 ring-blue-200/50 dark:ring-blue-700/50 group-hover:ring-blue-300/70 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg">
              <Image src={software} alt="IEC 62304 Medical Device Software Development" format={"svg"} class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-blue-500 dark:group-hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors duration-300" />
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-700 dark:group-hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors duration-300">Software Engineering</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Software development, firmware, real-time control systems, and safety-critical applications.
