            <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Embedded firmware development</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Real-time control software</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Desktop and web applications</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Safety-critical software design</li>
