              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Performance optimization</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-purple-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Manufacturing transition</li>
